          <div class="faq-answer">For most small businesses, theStacc is the top pick because it doesn't just schedule — it creates and publishes 30 original posts per month for $49/mo. Among pure scheduling tools, Buffer leads for simplicity. For agencies, Sendible or SocialPilot offer better multi-client management. For engagement, Agorapulse has the strongest social inbox.</div>
        </div>
